dct_title_s: Plan of Town Lots Belonging to Brigantine Improvement Company
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from St. Louis Avenue to Chester Avenue along the Atlantic Ocean.
Map shows the plan of the town lots layout in North Atlantic City. Map also shows the highwater line of the Atlantic Ocean.
